---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout activeKey="about" title="La comunidad · Boquete" titleEn="The community · Boquete">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="pad-sec" style="max-width:1240px;margin:0 auto;padding:70px 26px 20px">
    <div class="split-2" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:54px;align-items:center">
      <div class="rv">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B95C36;margin-bottom:16px">
          <span class="lang-es">La comunidad</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>The community</span>
        </div>
        <h1 style="font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(38px,5vw,62px);line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin:0 0 22px;color:#251D14">
          <span class="lang-es">Un pueblo de montaña con alma de café</span>
          <span class="lang-en" hidden>A mountain town with the soul of coffee</span>
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.62;color:#5A4F42;margin:0">
          <span class="lang-es">Fundado por colonos y pueblos originarios en las faldas del Volcán Barú, Boquete creció alrededor del café, las flores y un clima de primavera eterna que enamora a quien lo visita.</span>
          <span class="lang-en" hidden>Founded by settlers and Indigenous peoples on the slopes of Barú Volcano, Boquete grew around coffee, flowers and an eternal-spring climate that captivates everyone who visits.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv" style="position:relative;aspect-ratio:4/4.4;border-radius:22px;overflow:hidden">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/boquete-town-view/800/880" alt="Vista de Boquete" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HISTORY & CULTURE -->
  <section class="pad-sec" style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 26px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:64px">
    <!-- History -->
    <div class="split-2 rv" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:46px;align-items:center">
      <div style="position:relative;aspect-ratio:4/3;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/boquete-history/800/600" alt="Historia de Boquete" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8964A;margin-bottom:10px">
          <span class="lang-es">Historia</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>History</span>
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:700;font-size:30px;margin:0 0 14px;color:#251D14;letter-spacing:-.01em">
          <span class="lang-es">De colonos a capital del café</span>
          <span class="lang-en" hidden>From settlers to coffee capital</span>
        </h2>
        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.66;color:#5A4F42;margin:0">
          <span class="lang-es">Boquete se fundó oficialmente en 1911, aunque el valle ya era habitado por el pueblo Ngäbe. La llegada de inmigrantes europeos y el auge del café transformaron estas montañas en un próspero centro agrícola que hoy conserva su carácter tranquilo y acogedor.</span>
          <span class="lang-en" hidden>Boquete was officially founded in 1911, though the valley was already home to the Ngäbe people. The arrival of European immigrants and the coffee boom turned these mountains into a thriving agricultural hub that today keeps its calm, welcoming character.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Culture -->
    <div class="split-2 rv" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:46px;align-items:center">
      <div style="order:2">
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8964A;margin-bottom:10px">
          <span class="lang-es">Cultura</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>Culture</span>
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:700;font-size:30px;margin:0 0 14px;color:#251D14;letter-spacing:-.01em">
          <span class="lang-es">Un cruce de tradiciones</span>
          <span class="lang-en" hidden>A crossroads of traditions</span>
        </h2>
        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.66;color:#5A4F42;margin:0">
          <span class="lang-es">La identidad de Boquete mezcla la herencia indígena Ngäbe-Buglé, la cultura campesina chiricana y la influencia de comunidades de todo el mundo que eligieron estas montañas como hogar.</span>
          <span class="lang-en" hidden>Boquete's identity blends Ngäbe-Buglé Indigenous heritage, the rural culture of Chiriquí and the influence of communities from around the world who chose these mountains as home.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="position:relative;aspect-ratio:4/3;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/boquete-culture/800/600" alt="Cultura local" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three cards -->
    <div class="cols-3 rv" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:26px">
      {[
        { seed: 'traditions', labelEs: 'Tradiciones', labelEn: 'Traditions', titleEs: 'Flores, café y fiesta', titleEn: 'Flowers, coffee and festivity', bodyEs: 'Cada enero, la Feria de las Flores y del Café llena el pueblo de jardines, aromas y música. Es la expresión máxima de una comunidad orgullosa de su tierra y de su trabajo.', bodyEn: 'Every January, the Flower & Coffee Festival fills the town with gardens, aromas and music. It is the ultimate expression of a community proud of its land and its work.' },
        { seed: 'gastronomy', labelEs: 'Gastronomía', labelEn: 'Cuisine', titleEs: 'Sabor de las tierras altas', titleEn: 'Flavour of the highlands', bodyEs: 'Trucha fresca de río, hojaldres recién hechos, frutas de altura y, por supuesto, café de especialidad. La cocina de Boquete celebra los productos de su propia montaña.', bodyEn: 'Fresh river trout, just-made hojaldres, highland fruit and, of course, specialty coffee. Boquete\'s cuisine celebrates the produce of its own mountains.' },
        { seed: 'crafts', labelEs: 'Artesanías', labelEn: 'Crafts', titleEs: 'Manos que tejen identidad', titleEn: 'Hands that weave identity', bodyEs: 'Las chácaras y chaquiras del pueblo Ngäbe, tejidas a mano con fibras y cuentas de colores, son piezas únicas que llevan siglos de tradición en cada nudo.', bodyEn: 'The chácaras and chaquiras of the Ngäbe people, hand-woven with fibres and colourful beads, are unique pieces carrying centuries of tradition in every knot.' },
      ].map(card => (
        <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(37,29,20,.09);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden">
          <div style="position:relative;aspect-ratio:3/2;overflow:hidden">
            <img src={`https://picsum.photos/seed/${card.seed}/600/400`} alt={card.titleEs} style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div style="padding:20px">
            <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.13em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8964A;margin-bottom:8px">
              <span class="lang-es">{card.labelEs}</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>{card.labelEn}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:700;font-size:20px;margin:0 0 10px;color:#251D14">
              <span class="lang-es">{card.titleEs}</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>{card.titleEn}</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.6;color:#5A4F42;margin:0">
              <span class="lang-es">{card.bodyEs}</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>{card.bodyEn}</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO GET THERE -->
  <section style="background:#2C3A2A;margin-top:74px">
    <div class="pad-sec" style="max-width:1240px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 26px">
      <div class="split-2" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:46px;align-items:center">
        <div style="color:#F7F1E6">
          <div style="font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8964A;margin-bottom:12px">
            <span class="lang-es">Ubicación</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>Location</span>
          </div>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(28px,3.4vw,40px);margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-.01em">
            <span class="lang-es">Ubicación y cómo llegar</span>
            <span class="lang-en" hidden>Location and how to get there</span>
          </h2>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:#CFC6B2;margin:0 0 28px">
            <span class="lang-es">Boquete está a unos 40 minutos de la ciudad de David, capital de la provincia de Chiriquí, y a unas 7 horas por carretera desde la Ciudad de Panamá. El aeropuerto internacional Enrique Malek (David) recibe vuelos diarios.</span>
            <span class="lang-en" hidden>Boquete is about 40 minutes from David, capital of Chiriquí province, and roughly 7 hours by road from Panama City. Enrique Malek International Airport (David) receives daily flights.</span>
          </p>
          <div class="cols-3" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px">
            {[
              { icon: '✈', labelEs: 'En avión', labelEn: 'By air', bodyEs: 'Vuela a David (DAV) y conduce 40 min a Boquete.', bodyEn: 'Fly to David (DAV) and drive 40 min to Boquete.' },
              { icon: '🚗', labelEs: 'En auto', labelEn: 'By car', bodyEs: '7 h desde Ciudad de Panamá por la Interamericana.', bodyEn: '7 h from Panama City via the Pan-American Highway.' },
              { icon: '🚌', labelEs: 'En bus', labelEn: 'By bus', bodyEs: 'Buses directos desde la terminal de David cada 25 min.', bodyEn: 'Direct buses from David terminal every 25 min.' },
            ].map(t => (
              <div style="background:rgba(247,241,230,.08);border:1px solid rgba(247,241,230,.16);border-radius:14px;padding:18px">
                <div style="font-size:22px;margin-bottom:8px">{t.icon}</div>
                <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:6px">
                  <span class="lang-es">{t.labelEs}</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>{t.labelEn}</span>
                </div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;color:#B7AD98;line-height:1.5">
                  <span class="lang-es">{t.bodyEs}</span><span class="lang-en" hidden>{t.bodyEn}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative;aspect-ratio:4/3.4;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(247,241,230,.16)">
          <iframe
            title="Mapa Boquete"
            src="https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=-82.47%2C8.74%2C-82.40%2C8.81&layer=mapnik&marker=8.7798%2C-82.4419"
            style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0;filter:saturate(.85)"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
